high_descs: Go across the room to the counter past the stove.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Move over to the stove.
Put the ladle in the skillet on the back left burner of the stove.
Pick up the skillet with the ladle in it.
Go to the table by the door.
Set the skillet with the ladle inside down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a skillet with a ladle in it onto the table.

high_descs: Turn left, cross room, turn left to face counter.
Pick up ladle from counter.
Turn left, walk to stove, turn right to face stove.
Put ladle in bowl on back burner.
Pick up bowl with ladle in it.
Turn right, turn right again, walk to table, turn right to face table.
Place bowl with ladle in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put bowl with ladle in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the coffee maker across the room and then turn left and face the counter that is to the right of the stove
Pick up the ladle that is sitting on the counter
Turn left and walk to the stove
Place the ladle in the skillet that is on top of the stove; the skillet on the back left burner
Pick up the skillet that contains the ladle
Turn around and walk to the black fridge across the room, then hang right and talk to the white table that is on your left
Place the skillet containing the ladle on the table
anns.task_desc: Place a skillet containing a ladle on a table
